%global packname  mcgibbsit
%global packver   1.1.0
%global rlibdir   /usr/local/lib/R/library

Name:             R-CRAN-%{packname}
Version:          1.1.0
Release:          3%{?dist}
Summary:          Warnes and Raftery's MCGibbsit MCMC diagnostic

License:          GPL
URL:              https://cran.r-project.org/package=%{packname}
Source0:          %{url}&version=%{packver}#/%{packname}_%{packver}.tar.gz


BuildRequires:    R-devel
Requires:         R-core
BuildArch:        noarch
BuildRequires:    R-CRAN-coda 
Requires:         R-CRAN-coda 

%description
'mcgibbsit' provides an implementation of Warnes & Raftery's MCGibbsit
run-length diagnostic for a set of (not-necessarily independent) MCMC
samplers.  It combines the estimate error-bounding approach of the Raftery
and Lewis MCMC run length diagnostic with the between verses within chain
approach of the Gelman and Rubin MCMC convergence diagnostic.

